You force your way along the rough path—fast, but careless.
[[Something stirs in the brush->Minor Encounter]]

:: Minor Encounter [Act0 Combat]
A shape lunges—eyes too bright, hide too thin. Blackwood’s creatures are **wrong**.

* [[Fight through->After Minor Encounter]]
* [[Try to slip past (Stealth)->Stealth Past]]

