:: After Minor Encounter [Act0 Combat]
(Combat placeholder)
You survive and press on.
[[Continue->Wounded Bandit Leader]]

:: Wounded Bandit Leader [Act0 Dialogue]
In a small clearing, the **bandit leader** slumps against a tree—badly injured. A scar cuts one cheek like a cruel signature.

He coughs, then grins through blood.
''Bandit:'' “Too late… hero.”

Ask (choose any order):
* [[“Where’s the rest of your gang?”->Bandit Q1]]
* [[“Where are the stolen goods?”->Bandit Q2]]
* [[[Intimidate] “Talk, or I finish what the forest started.”->Bandit Intimidate]]
* [[[Heal/Medicine] “Hold still. I can help.”->Bandit Heal]]
* [[“I’m here for justice.” (Start combat)->Bandit Combat]]

:: Bandit Q1 [Act0 Dialogue]
''Bandit:'' “They abandoned me. Funny, isn’t it? Loyalty’s just a word when teeth are at your throat.”
[[Back->Wounded Bandit Leader]]

:: Bandit Q2 [Act0 Dialogue]
''Bandit:'' “Camp ahead. Hidden. You’ll smell it before you see it.”
[[Back->Wounded Bandit Leader]]

:: Bandit Intimidate [Act0 Dialogue]
''Bandit:'' “All right—ALL right. Camp ahead. And… a letter. For **Oakhaven**. ‘The package’. ‘The tower’… that’s all I know!”
[[Back->Wounded Bandit Leader]]

:: Bandit Heal [Act0 Dialogue]
You bind the worst of it. He breathes easier—then his eyes harden.

''Bandit:'' “Shouldn’t have done that.”
[[Combat begins->Bandit Combat]]

:: Bandit Combat [Act0 Combat]
(Combat placeholder)
<<if $hasWeapon>>
