The **Old Watchtower** rises, cracked and hungry. Its entrance is sealed by a shimmering barrier.

''The Elder:'' “A harmony lock. Three tones to break the song.”

Find **three Singing Stones** in the rubble.

* [[Search the fallen arch->Find Stone A]]
* [[Dig through a collapsed shrine->Find Stone B]]
* [[Check the weed-choked well->Find Stone C]]
* [[Try the barrier->Try Barrier]]

