:: Act 4 Entry [Act4 Entry]
**ACT 4 — The Void Sanctum**

A ritual hangs over a void. Sorath waits behind a shield of emerald force.

[[Enter the sanctum->Void Sanctum]]

:: Void Sanctum [Act4 Dialogue]
A cavern yawns wide. Floating rocks drift above an infinite void. Emerald light blinds.

At the centre, **Sorath** floats—channeling a ritual. A shield surrounds him.

''Sorath:'' “Ah… a living witness. How rare.”

Phase 1:
* [[Endure the waves of skeletons->Phase 1 Waves]]

:: Phase 1 Waves [Act4 Combat]
(Combat waves placeholder)

Time passes. The shield flickers.
<<set $sorathShieldDown to true>>

[[The shield drops—now!->Phase 2 Sorath]]

:: Phase 2 Sorath [Act4 Combat]
Sorath moves like a thought. Ice and necrotic power coil from his hands.

(Combat placeholder)

You land what should be the final blow—Sorath collapses into dust… then reforms instantly.

''Sorath:'' “Did you think that was enough?”

* [[Use the Sun-Shard to disrupt the ritual core->Use Sun-Shard]]
* [[Try to defeat him by force alone->Force Alone]]

