<<if $sunShard>>
You raise the Sun-Shard. Light floods the void—pure, intolerant.

Sorath screams—not in pain, but in **fear**.
The ritual threads snap. His form fractures.

<<set $sorathTrueDefeated to true>>
[[Epilogue->Epilogue]]
<<else>>
