:: Force Alone [Act4 Outcome]
Your blows scatter him… but he returns, stronger, laughing.

''The Elder:'' “He is bound to the ritual. Sever it—or he will always return.”

**END (Partial victory / Sorath persists)**

:: Epilogue [Act4 Outcome]
Sorath crumbles into true dust. The emerald hum dies. Silence returns.

You find a hoard, and **Sorath’s Grimoire** among blackened relics.

''The Elder:'' “From ruin, a beacon. From you… a legend.”

**END (True victory)**
